{
  "verses": [
    {
      "n": 29,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Jehkab̄ waizaja un\nfazzija: Paſakki man/ luhdsams/\ntavu Wahrdü / un tas fazzija:\nKam tu jauta pehz mannu Wahrdü/ un tas fwehtija winnu turpatt.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 30,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Jehkab̄ noſauze tahs\nWeetas Wahrdü Pniël/jo/(faz-\nzija tas) es eſmu Deewu ne\nWaiga Waigain redſejis / un\nmannu Dwehfele irr iſglahbta.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 31,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un ta Saute uslehze tam/\npehz to/ kad wiꞥſch Pnuëtu bij\nfezzen gahjts; un wiꞥſch klibbo-\nja ar ſawu Zifku.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 32,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tapehz ne ehd Iſraëla\nBehrni no Dſihfles pee Ziskas Loh-\nektta/lihds ſchodeen / tapehz / ka\nJehkabam ta Dſihfle pee Ziskas\nlohzekta maitata tappa.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Wn Jehkab̄ pazehſe fa-\nwäs Azzis/ un ſkatti-\njahs/ un reds/ Eẜaws\nahze/ un tfchetrfſimts Wihri ar\nto: Tad peefchihre wiꞥſch tohs\nBehrnuſ pee Leas/ un pee Raë-\nks/un pee tahm diwi Kalponehim.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 2,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un likke tahs Kalpones un\nwinnu Behrnuſ papreeſſch / un\npeii un winna Behrnuſ pakkat\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un wiꞥſch patsgahje teen\npreekſcha / un klannijahs feptin-\nreifi pee Semmes/teekans wiꞥſ-\npee ſawa Brahta klaht tappe.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Eḝaws tezzeja tah\npretti un apkaimpeto/ un uietteh\napkahrt winna Raflu/ un skuyp\nſtija to/ un tee raudaja.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un wiꞥſch pazehſe ſawa\nAzzis/ un redſeja tahs Seewas,\nun tohs Behrmis / un fazzija\nKam peederr tee/ kas pee tew/ un\ntas fazzija : (ſchee irr) tee Behr-\nni / fo Deews tawani Kalpan\nirr eedahivanajs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad peegahje tahs Kalpo-\nnes/ winnas/ un winno Behrni,\nun paſlannijahs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Lea peegahje arridſan\nun winnas Behrni / un paſlan-\nnijahs / un pehz nahze Jahsep-\nun Räele/ un paſlannijahs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un wiꞥſch fazzija: Kam\nwiſs tas Lehgeris / ko es fastap-\npig eſmu? un tas fazzija: Kaes\nSchehlaſtibu atrohmu tawas Az-\nzis/ mans Kungs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Eḝaws fazzija: Man\npascham gann irr/ mans Brah-\nli / paturr / kas tew peederr.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Bet Jehkab̄ fazzija : At-\nne! luhdsams/ ja es Schehlaſtibu\neſmu atraddiſtawäs Azzis/ tad\nzem mannu Dahwann no man-\nnas Rohkas; jo tapehz eſmu es-\n"
    }
  ],
  "confidence": "high",
  "notes": ""
}
